        "timestamp": "2021-01-15 14:19:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1\n\nThis commit means having 100% coverage for one module, which is practically not possible. We may sometime want to split a commit in two parts, like tests separate or maybe just entities before. this would not allow that. i am ok with current global coverage. instead of this, we should write more tests and have global coverage of 85-90%.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
